OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain continuing across Scotland and
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland tonight, with the odd
OL,8,Fthunderstorm across the far southeast
OL,9,Fof England. Otherwise a warm and muggy
OL,10,Fnight, with areas of mist and log
OL,11,Fcloud, especially towards the
OL,12,Fsouthwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FSpells of rain in the
OL,15,Fnorthwest edging slowly southeast with
OL,16,Fshowers following. Drier elsewhere
OL,17,Fwith sunny spells. Very warm or hot in
OL,18,Fthe southeast and feeling muggy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
